{"tid":888010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［選舉前敲詐］北韓：若美不撤經濟制裁 或恢復發展核武","createTime":"2018-11-03T11:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T14:44:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64c633eb57cc63619546efea3e8493596594ec35","tid":888010,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"北韓警告，美國若不解除對平壤的經濟制裁，北韓或會恢復發展核武。<br />\n<br />\n北韓外交部發聲明，指實施制裁及改善關係並不相容，又稱美方不斷重申「制裁和施壓」會達至半島無核化，認為是「可笑及愚蠢」。相反解除制裁，是回應北韓積極及善意的行動。<br />\n<br />\n北韓方面強調，若美國不改變立場，並正確理解北韓的意願，北韓可能會恢復，同時發展核力量及經濟的「並進」政策。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿 Pompeo 較早前表示，美國會繼續施加經濟壓力，直至北韓領袖金正恩履行 6 月美朝峰會上、對總統特朗普的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #北韓 #美國 #核武 #制裁 #經濟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/1893278500709711/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F1893278500709711%2F&d=QJiBFdIC7ga6j01jlL1Mwxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6e6b9579\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/1893278500709711/</a>"},{"pid":"c6eda0e3498538711a4ff0abda1f616a38d0d7d2","tid":888010,"uid":56323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"比美國佬撚完又浦返水面出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1636e9f57c2867e4827a6688de9a2a6cce6013","tid":888010,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"南韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cd6687d0ac710aa0d3f2558cd17ee847f1ada0","tid":888010,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6eda0e3498538711a4ff0abda1f616a38d0d7d2","tid":888010,"uid":56323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"比美國佬撚完又浦返水面出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im